[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The threats from natural events in space are well understood
[normal] and ESA has an on-going programme to provide monitoring and 
[normal]warnings of Space Weather events
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]6.6.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The loss of space assets has a similar impact whether from natural events or deliberate actions.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] The focus must be on things we can control
[normal] –
[normal] 
[normal]impact 
[normal]mitigation within the national infrastructure. Government should:
